# claude-picker demo recording
# Run: vhs demo.tape
# Output: demo.gif

Output demo.gif
Output demo.webm

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Type "claude-picker"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Navigate project picker
Down
Sleep 300ms
Up
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Navigate session picker
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Up
Sleep 400ms
Up
Sleep 400ms

# Wait to show preview panel
Sleep 2s

Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms

# Select a session
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 2s
